network.param.modules.workflowConsensus

Class WorkflowConsensus

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.param.modules.workflowConsensus.WorkflowConsensus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBean, IWorkflowConsensus

    public final class WorkflowConsensus
extends java.lang.Object
implements IWorkflowConsensus
    Implementation of IWorkflowConsensus, this class represents the Param workflow consensus information.

    This Class IWorkflowConsensus will represents workflow consensus field IWorkflowConsensus defines below categories of operations:

    • setWorkflowID method to set workflow Id.

    • getWorkflowID method to get the workflow Id.

    • setMetaData method set metadata.

    • getMetaData method get metadata.

    • setDocumentIDS method set doc Id.

    • getDocumentIDS method get doc Id.

    • setCurrentStep method set current step.

    • getCurrentStep method get current step.

    • setTxnMode method set TxnMode.

    • getTxnMode method get Txn mode.

    • setMergeID method Set merge Id.

    • getMergeID method get merge Id

    • setCompleted method to set workflow completed.

    • isCompleted method get workflow is completed.

    • setStepSigners method set workflow step signer.

    • setOwner method set owner.

    • setPrimaryOwner method set primary owner.

    • addStepSigners method add workflow step signers.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
